documentation.text:
Following measures are considered here:
1. Only whitelist flags means only allow whitelist transactions.
2. If the auto blacklist flag is set, automatically blacklist people after buy.
3. If the ignore blacklist flag is set, ignore the blacklist. We blacklist offenders on the main
   contract and open it up here.
4. If cap is set limit buy to the cap.
Note that this is a temporary safety locker that would be removed after a while, so we don't
necessarily care about gas saving.
Return true should shortcircuit. Returns true for whitelist
